-- Thai Court Says Water Projects Must Be Subject to Public Hearing
-- B y   S u p u n n a b u l   S u w a n n a k i j
-- 2013-06-27T09:51:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-06-27/thai-court-says-water-projects-must-be-subject-to-public-hearing.html
The Thai Administrative Court ruled
today that the government must conduct a public hearing and
environmental and health impact studies before moving ahead with
any water-management projects in  Thailand .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Supunnabul Suwannakij in Bangkok at 
 ssuwannakij@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
